{
  "stem": "25938.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A very small room, and we lived there till-- till 1940-- '42, I think.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, from that ghetto, we were sent-- I can't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "From that ghetto barrack, we were sent-- sent to Kielbasin, that little-- that camp, Kielbasin.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In ghetto, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had-- Mother use to sell-- people selled-- sold whatever they had.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they went to the peasants, and they-- and they-- they changed it for-- for-- for milk or for something.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No one.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were no guards.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were-- we were living there, and--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "People kept hoping that the world would put an end to the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To us, it was a new word.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just read in literature about the Jewish ghettos in-- in-- in-- in the Middle Ages, or something in England, or I mean, Spain, or where.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "To-- to us, it was just a-- again, in that-- we didn't-- ghetto was-- the Germans created that ghetto.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They called it a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, there was no-- nowhere to run, because-- because we couldn't go to the Polish population.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had to go to sleep.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where-- where-- where will we go?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We used to go to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- the--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All kinds, chop the wood, do all kinds of work, yeah.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We worked for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was fear.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was constant-- we lived constantly in constant fear.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They used to come.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They used to come to the ghetto, and just shoot, just in-- in the air to frighten the people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Terrorize the people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were not beaten or something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was-- you know, people-- people didn't think of anything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I, myself, didn't think of anything, we just-- it was like a relief from-- for when they got out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
